{
  "stem": "4361.9",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, they want you to be president of, of the Hadassah chapter in New York.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I matriculated at Sarah Lawrence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had continuing education courses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got two years of college because although I didn't have any papers to prove that I had a baccalaureate diploma, my name was found in a book written by the chief rabbi of Kolozsvar, who listed all the students in the last grade.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my name was there, and so they gave me two years And the 60 credits that I had to take for the next two years, I think I made it in six months.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And but then, something happened at Sarah Lawrence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I met a writer by the name of Saul Yurick, Y-U-R-I-C-K-- not Saul, Sal, S-A-L.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I started to write short stories, which was part of the course I was taking, and I decided I really want to write.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I gave up the law.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "However, when I went to Sarah Lawrence, the idea was that I'm going to get my degree and then go to law school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And once Sarah Lawrence accepted me, I went to-- I had an interview with the dean of the law-- of law school at Columbia, where-- of which my husband is a graduate.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I told him, I've been accepted and I would like to go to law school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are my chances because I am not a young woman, et cetera, et cetera?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said, all that matters are grades.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So fine, I said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But what happened at Sarah Lawrence?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I s-- somehow, I began to write, and I gave up law, the idea of being a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'm sure much to my husband's relief.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And that's what I am doing since.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
